bio: "Sasuke Sarutobi, father of Hiruzen Sarutobi, grandfather of Asuma Sarutobi and his brother, great grandfather of Mirai Sarutobiand Konohamaru Sarutobi, he is also the great grandfather in law of Konohamarus mom. Sasuke sarutobi was once a great shinobi of the hidden leaf village. No other information is known about him.",
